{"id:": "/div[1]", "tag": "div", "attributes": {"type": "article", "{http://www.w3.org/XML/1998/namespace}id": "MG-1679-07_111", "resp": "mercure"}, "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]", "tag": "head", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Au Roy. Sonnet"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]", "tag": "bibl", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]", "tag": "title", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Mercure galant"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/text()[1]", "text": ", juillet 1679 [tome 7], p. 111-114."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Je vous envoye deux Sonnets que j’ay reçeus d’Allemagne. Ils sont tous deux sur la Paix, quoy que diférens de stile. M"}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "r"}], "attributes": {"rend": "sup"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/text()[2]", "text": " de la Barre Matéï en est l’Autheur. C'est un Gentilhomme d’un fort grand mérite, auquel Sa Majesté, par estime particuliere, a témoigné avoir envie de faire du bien. C'est là-dessus qu’il a fait le premier de ces Sonnets. Il fut presenté au Roy ces jours passez par une Personne de tres-grande qualité. Le second est un Inpromptu pour M"}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/hi[2]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/hi[2]/text()[1]", "text": "r"}], "attributes": {"rend": "sup"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/text()[3]", "text": " le Comte de Louvigny, qui, comme vous sçavez, est un des plus braves Hommes qu’il y ait dans le Party de l’Empereur. Il y a peu de temps qu’il traita magnifiquement toute la Cour de Monsieur le Duc de Hannover, dans son Quartier sur le chemin d’Embs, où ce Prince alloit aux Eaux. M"}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/hi[3]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/hi[3]/text()[1]", "text": "r"}], "attributes": {"rend": "sup"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/text()[4]", "text": " de la Barre Matéï estoit du Régal, & fit ce Sonnet en buvant à la santé de ce fameux Commandant."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]", "tag": "label", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Au Roy."}], "attributes": {"type": "head"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[2]", "tag": "label", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Sonnet."}], "attributes": {"type": "head"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Ta bonté se répand sur la Terre & sur l’Onde,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Et remplit l’Univers des douceurs de la Paix."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Que de Peuples heureux vont joüir desormais"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Des Biens que leur promet cette source féconde !"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[5]", "tag": "l", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/ab[1]", "tag": "ab", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/ab[1]/text()[1]", "text": "***"}], "attributes": {"type": "ornament"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[6]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[6]/text()[1]", "text": "Sur elle mon espoir, comme le leur, se fonde,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[7]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[7]/text()[1]", "text": "Et j’en attens un jour d’infaillibles effets ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[8]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[8]/text()[1]", "text": "J'ay sujet de prétendre aux graces que tu fais,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[9]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[9]/text()[1]", "text": "Lors que tu prens plaisir d’en combler tout le monde."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[10]", "tag": "l", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/ab[2]", "tag": "ab", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/ab[2]/text()[1]", "text": "***"}], "attributes": {"type": "ornament"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[11]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[11]/text()[1]", "text": "Tu voulus autrefois m’honorer d’un bienfait."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[12]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[12]/text()[1]", "text": "As-tu pú le vouloir sans qu’il m’ait esté fait,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[13]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[13]/text()[1]", "text": "Et manqueray-je seul de place en ta mémoire ?"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[14]", "tag": "l", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/ab[3]", "tag": "ab", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/ab[3]/text()[1]", "text": "***"}], "attributes": {"type": "ornament"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[15]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[15]/text()[1]", "text": "Grand Roy, par deux raisons je t’en fais souvenir,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[16]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[16]/text()[1]", "text": "Il y va de mon bien, il y va de ta gloire,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[17]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[17]/text()[1]", "text": "Ce sont deux intérests que je dois maintenir."}]}]}]}